## [1.0.0] - June 2026
### Added
- Initial release of the nutanix_vm Terraform module
- Unified VM provisioning module supporting both template path
  (nutanix_deploy_templates_v2) and image path (nutanix_virtual_machine)
  via the source_type variable
- All 10 mandatory HLD Nutanix categories enforced as required inputs
- Dynamic naming logic: UMICORE_LOCATION-usage_code-NNNN
- vm_name_override support for acquired/migrated site legacy hostnames
- Guest customisation: Sysprep (Windows), cloud-init (Linux),
  none (appliances)
- Data disk support via data_disks variable
- Sub-resource naming for vDisks and vNICs derived from vm_name
